Transfer Students n n        Most commonly  transfer students choose Commons North  to live with students who are all     or the apartments on the south or west side of campus   For a more affordable option  students also choose to stay in Polk Street Residence  PSR  clusters on the west side of campus  n       n Transfer Students  nGraduate Professional n n        Graduate students primarily stay in Single Student Residence  SSR  located on the west side of campus   Apartments are also located on the south side of campus in Marie Robinson Hall  MRH  and Thomas Beckham Hall  TBH  n       n Graduate Professional  n nUIC Logo n n n n UIC Logo  n          Campus Housing n         Future Apply           Rates Residence Halls Services Why Live on Campus Current Academic Support Apply Get Involved ReApp Services Affiliate Conference Housing Guest Housing Intern Housing Medical Students Button Menu About Housing Contact Us Dock MyContract Student Affairs Contact                           housing uic edu Social Media Accounts  nFacebook n Facebook  nTwitter n Twitter  nInstagram n Instagram  nYouTube n YouTube UIC edu links UIC edu Academic Calendar Athletics Campus Directory Disability Resources Emergency Information Event Calendar Job Openings Library Maps UIC Today UI Health Veterans Affairs Privacy Statement Campuses University of Illinois System Urbana Champaign Springfield Cookie Settings 